ng>Ideal for creatives, designers, artists, photographers, showcase your portfolio…</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<div class=\"wpthemes_image_preview\"><a href=\"http://themeforest.net/item/bloom-responsive-wordpress-theme/full_screen_preview/2390368?ref=neel\" title=\"Download \"Bloom &#8211; Responsive WordPress Theme\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://wordpressskins.org/wp-content/themes/wpskinsnew/timthumb.php?src=http://wordpressskins.org/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/01_Preview.__large_preview3.jpg&a=t&w=500\"a lt=\"Bloom &#8211; Responsive WordPress Theme\" /></a></div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2>Light / Dark Style</h2>\n<p><a href=\"http://wordpressskins.org/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/darklight.png\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1730\" title=\"darklight\" src=\"http://wordpressskins.org/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/darklight.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"616\" height=\"397\" /></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2>Visual Shortcodes Editor</h2>\n<p>Bloom comes with a built-in visual shortcodes editor where you can preview the appearance of the page. Draw the page your way before anyone sees!</p>\n<h2>Fully Widgetized Homepage / Footer</h2>\n<p>Build your homepage with an incredible ease using the 10 custom Desginare widgets created exclusively for this theme.</p>\n<h2>Unlimited Portfolios</h2>\n<p>This theme come with a custom projects Structure where you can manage differents portfolios and respective projects.<br />\nYou can create unlimited portfolios and inside the portfolios you can create unlimited projects.</p>\n<h2>SEO optimized</h2>\n<p>Bloom has been prepared not only for user, but for search engines as well. All headings has been made in order (h1, h2, h3, &#8230;, h6) from the most important to less. You can easily customize the SEO info like the site title, keywords and description.</p>\n<h2>Theme Features</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Clean and OnePage Design</li>\n<li>Responsive Layout</li>\n<li>Unlimited Filterable Portfolios</li>\n<li>Display work with 2 different galleries</li>\n<li>Easily Create and Manage Photo and Video Collections</li>\n<li>Unlimited Color Skins</li>\n<li>SEO optimized</li>\n<li>Extensive Options Panel</li>\n<li>30+ Awesome Visual Shortcodes</li>\n<li>10 Custom and Exclusive Widgets</li>\n<li>2 Custom Post Structures (Projects and Testimonials)</li>\n<li>Working Ajax Contact Form</li>\n<li>Full WordPress 3.3 compatibility</li>\n<li>Translation Ready</li>\n<li>XML File with the Bloom WordPress demo</li>\n<li>Layered PSD Files</li>\n<li>and much more…</li>\n</ul>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:74:\"http://wordpressskins.org/1723/bloom-responsive-wordpress-theme.html/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:5;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:87:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:46:\"eVision – Blog and Portfolio WordPress Theme\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:74:\"http://wordpressskins.org/1721/evision-blog-portfolio-wordpress-theme.html\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:83:\"http://wordpressskins.org/1721/evision-blog-portfolio-wordpress-theme.html#commen