"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:5003:\"<p>Zine is a modern &amp; responsive review theme perfect for a magazine/blog/review site.<br />\nYou can choose the whole appareance of your website with the theme options panel and manage your content very easily with the 5 custom post types.<br />\nIt can be used as a portfolio or any other purpose as well.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<div class=\"wpthemes_image_preview\"><a href=\"http://themeforest.net/item/zine-modern-responsive-review-theme/full_screen_preview/2399603?ref=neel\" title=\"Download \"Zine &#8211; Modern &#038; Responsive Review Theme\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://wordpressskins.org/wp-content/themes/wpskinsnew/timthumb.php?src=http://wordpressskins.org/wp-content/uploads/2012/06/01_Preview.__large_preview2.jpg&a=t&w=500\"a lt=\"Zine &#8211; Modern &#038; Responsive Review Theme\" /></a></div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2>Last update</h2>\n<h5><strong>14 june 2012</strong> – Version 0.4</h5>\n<ol>\n<li>Update for WordPress 3.4 (removed deprecated functions)</li>\n</ol>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<h2>Features</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Instinctive admin interface</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Responsive</strong></li>\n<li><strong>5 Custom Post types</strong>:\n<ol>\n<li>Movie reviews</li>\n<li>Music reviews</li>\n<li>Video Game reviews</li>\n<li>Book reviews</li>\n<li>Portfolio</li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n<li><strong>4 menus locations</strong>: main menu, top menu and bottom menu + <strong>Mobile/Tablet Menu</strong><br />\nThe Top Menu and Main menu support <strong>3 levels drop down</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Custom backgrounds</strong>: You can upload a different background for each page directly in your page editor.</li>\n<li><strong>Archive template</strong> and <strong>custom taxonomies</strong> for each post types</li>\n<li><strong>Rating system</strong> and <strong>Top Rated templates</strong> for reviews post types</li>\n<li><strong>SEO </strong>feature : you can set up your metatags for each post and page.</li>\n<li>Generate <strong>video thumbnails</strong> automatically for video post format.</li>\n<li><strong>Filter Portfolio</strong> (izotope)</li>\n<li><strong>Complete Theme Options Panel</strong>: switch between the 2 pre-made skins (light or dark) , upload your backgrounds, logos, change fonts, change the colors with color pickers, set many options, set your social network profiles url etc… You can upload an advertisment header banner as well.</li>\n<li>Supports <strong>Post Formats</strong> for your blog (audio, video, image, gallery, link, quote, aside)</li>\n<li><strong>Unlimited sidebars</strong>: In addition to custom sidebars for each custom post types, you can create unlimited sidebars and choose which one you want to display on each page.</li>\n<li><strong>Slider manager</strong>: upload and reorder your image by drag’n drop, set captions etc…</li>\n<li><strong>10 Custom Widgets</strong>: No need to have a hundred of widget,<br />\n1) the <strong>“Post Types- All in one”</strong> widget allow you to choose the post type to display in your widget, as recent, most commented or featured articles, and choose if you want to display this articles previews as text link or link with a thumbnail or even a mini video for your video post types.<br />\n2) The <strong>“Taxonomy widget”</strong> allow you to display any custom categories (taxonmy) of any post types.<br />\n3) Other widgets: <strong>Twitter feed, facebook fanbox, social counter widget, flickr widget, video widget, network widget, advertisement widget, recent comment widget with avatars, custom tabs (recent, popular, comment)</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Advertisement manager</strong>: Upload and manage your advertisements and use the <strong>“advertisement widget”</strong> to display them anywhere in your sidebars very easily.</li>\n<li>A bunch of <strong>usefull shortcodes</strong> with custom editor buttons to generate them</li>\n<li><strong>Social Share buttons</strong>: facebook, twitter, google+, linkedIn, pinterest (meta automatically generated.</li>\n<li><strong>Social Plugin</strong> : Set links to your social network profiles in the theme options (<strong> available</strong>)</li>\n<li><strong>Author box and Author templates</strong> : extra profile fields added for your authors (twitter, facebook , google+, linkedIn, Digg, StumbleUpon, Flickr, Youtube)</li>\n<li><strong>Choose your Homepage</strong>:<br />\nChoose your home page header as slider, video, static image or no header<br />\nChoose wich post type you want to display (default is all post types)<br />\nIf you choose to display the last blog posts, you can choose to display only one category (e.g: news)</li>\n<li>Complete <strong>Documentation</strong> with screenshots.</li>\n<li>Automatically create the <strong>main pages on theme installation</strong>.</li>\n<li><strong>Translation Ready</strong> : Contains .po and .mo files for translation</li>\n<li>Built on the <strong>BrutalDesign Framework</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Support</strong>: I do my best to answer to all support requests</li>\n</ul>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:77:\"http://wordpressskins.org/1707/zine-modern-responsive-review-theme.html/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}}}s:27:\"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom\";a:1:{s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:3:{s:4:\"href\";s:31:\"http://wordpressskins.org/feed/\";s:3:\"rel\";s:4:\"self\";s:4:\"type\";s:19:\"application/rss+xml\";}}s:8:\"x