ps &amp; Awards:-</strong></p>\r\n<p lang=\"en-US\" style=\"text-align: left;\">    1) Rs 3000/- received from U.T. Chandigarh for State Medal 2011-12</p>\r\n<p lang=\"en-US\" style=\"text-align: left;\">    2) Rs 3000/- received from U.T. Chandigarh as prize money on National Sports day* for national achievements.</p>\r\n\r\n<h4 lang=\"en-US\" style=\"text-align: left; padding-left: 30px;\"><strong>ACADAMIC<strong>S:-</strong>-</strong></h4>\r\n<p lang=\"en-US\" style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>  </strong>1) All Rounder Trophy in 4<sup>th</sup> class in 2011-12.</p>\r\n<p lang=\"en-US\" style=\"text-align: left;\">  2) Two Gold medals (Science &amp; Maths. Olympiad (Class-5) for School Rank -1 in 1<sup>st </sup>Round ).</p>\r\n<p lang=\"en-US\" style=\"text-align: left;\">  3) State Rank -7 in Science Olympiad held for 2<sup>nd</sup> Round.</p>\r\n<p lang=\"en-US\" style=\"text-align: left;\">  4) Best Student Trophy in Class 5<sup>th</sup> (2012-13).</p>\r\n<p lang=\"en-US\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>* Honored by U.T. Sports Council (Chandigarh) for National Achievents of 2012-13 at function</em></p>\r\n<p lang=\"en-US\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>held on 29-08-2013 at Skating Rink Sec-10 , Chandigarh.</em></p>','SAKSHAM BANSAL ','Sachin Ramesh Tendulkar AM (Listeni/səˈtʃɪn tɛnˈduːlkər/; born 24 April 1973)[1] is an Indian cricketer widely acknowledged as one of the greatest batsmen in cricket.','inherit','open','open','','73-autosave-v1','','','2013-09-02 11:43:41','2013-09-02 11:43:41','',73,'http://localhost/rollingtiger/73-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(86,1,'2013-08-29 09:46:42','2013-08-29 09:46:42','','Dhoni_at_Reebok_event','','inherit','open','open','','dhoni_at_reebok_event','','','2013-08-29 09:46:42','2013-08-29 09:46:42','',21,'http://localhost/rollingtiger/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/Dhoni_at_Reebok_event.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(87,1,'2013-08-29 10:09:32','2013-08-29 10:09:32','<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-imag